3v", "ext": "mp4", "width": 1080, "height": 1920, "tbr": 2194.943, "format_note": "DASH video", "container": "mp4_dash", "vcodec": "vp09.00.40.08.00.01.01.01.00", "acodec": "none", "dynamic_range": "SDR", "url": "https://scontent-mia5-1.cdninstagram.com/o1/v/t2/f2/m367/AQMHZnt5-SDCjCEZSy3F4RrXJZxHP7bu-5drsmlcvfBPMb1mKooUrPRX9PdJ_TGEuc42FDHQCc0sYIVDn11CkhWPqVrx8DgRxOuOsyw.mp4?_nc_cat=101&_nc_sid=9ca052&_nc_ht=scontent-mia5-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_ohc=D2ZCn-7pA0EQ7kNvwFECZWY&%3D%3D&ccb=17-1&_nc_gid=lKhwABsmidDr-WFTZgqOhw&_nc_zt=28&_nc_ss=7a22e&oh=00_Af7abn10sDx8HWEyYrKiNPqx1iK0Bx9N5ML9ZAcz8Zd8BA&oe=6A1E3E6A", "manifest_stream_number": 0, "is_dash_periods": true, "protocol": "https", "video_ext": "mp4", "audio_ext": "none", "abr": 0, "vbr": 2194.943, "resolution": "1080x1920", "aspect_ratio": 0.56, "filesize_approx": 14440804, "http_headers": {"User-Agent": "Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/143.0.0.0 Safari/537.36", "Accept": "text/html,application/xhtml+xml,application/xml;q=0.9,*/*;q=0.8", "Accept-Language": "en-us,en;q=0.5", "Sec-Fetch-Mode": "navigate", "Referer": "https://www.instagram.com/"}, "format": "dash-1551271939311823v - 1080x1920 (DASH video)"}], "title": "Video by bilawal.ai", "description": "Comment ‘3d’ to learn how I made this. God’s eye view 24-hour replay of Operation Epic Fury.\n\nThe Iran strikes kicked off and I set an AI agent swarm loose to record every OSINT signal I could find before the caches cleared. Built a full 4D reconstruction in WorldView.\n\nI can scrub through minute by minute and watch the whole thing unfold on a 3D globe:\n\n> Airspace clearing over Tehran\n> Ground strike coordinates locking in\n> Severe GPS interference blinding the region\n> EO and SAR satellites making passes over the strike zone\n> No-fly zones locking down 9 countries\n> Shipping fleets scrambling at the Strait of Hormuz\n\nIt’s pretty amazing how complete of a picture you can build without “proprietary data fusion” — one dev with public signals and a love for computer graphics and geospatial intelligence.\n\nThank you for all the love on my last post. Dropping WorldView in April. This my friends is just the beginning.\n\n#ai #3d #photogrammetry #futuretech #osint", "duration": 52.633, "timestamp": 1772399169, "uploader_id": "18039316", "uploader": "Bilawal Sidhu", "channel": "bilawal.ai", "like_count": 9577, "comment_count": 2004, "comments": [{"author": "g.s_94", "author_id": "6745782656", "id": "18130654732569630", "text": "3D", "timestamp": 1779465516}, {"author": "haizoun_mohamed.ae", "author_id": "45246393171", "id": "18266891104295445", "text": "3d", "timestamp": 1779095520}, {"author": "clay.smith.co", "author_id": "39034827459", "id": "18064063463405324", "text": "3D", "timestamp": 1778648120}, {"author": "erwanabumusa", "author_id": "3574550052", "id": "18090578057364606", "text": "3d", "timestamp": 1778502398}, {"author": "_6alu", "author_id": "12061178874", "id": "17983495829822590", "text": "3d", "timestamp": 1777742980}, {"author": "controlmedia_ia", "author_id": "76194836385", "id": "18102004709052480", "text": "3d", "timestamp": 1777670992}, {"author": "tanguy_stradivari", "author_id": "2239709793", "id": "18419959753124874", "text": "3D", "timestamp": 1777008338}, {"author": "lcrojano", "author_id": "2344776101", "id": "18141218728502828", "text": "3d", "timestamp": 1776954810}, {"author": "sukhoiberkut47", "author_id": "71659160211", "id": "18078005987296028", "text": "3D", "timestamp": 1776781833}, {"author": "sukhoiberkut47", "author_id": "71659160211", "id": "17887004910472968", "text": "3D", "timestamp": 1776781833}], "thumbnails": [{"url": "https://scontent-mia3-2.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/641753727_1427086945548975_143379254074860173_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi42NDAuc2RyLnZpZGVvX25mcmFtZV9jb3Zlcl9mcmFtZS5jMiJ9&_nc_ht=scontent-mia3-2.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=103&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gFiT4acgxAS0fx-W7AfZjgY